OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMan charged over Bradley   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FLowery football 'taunt'    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man has been charged after reports an
OL,6, image of Bradley Lowery was used to    
OL,7, taunt opposition football fans.        
OL,9,FThe alleged incident happened at       
OL,10,FSheffield Wednesday's home game on     
OL,11,FFriday against Sunderland - the team   
OL,12,Fthe six-year-old boy supported before  
OL,13,Fhe died of cancer in 2017.             
OL,15,FDale Houghton, 31, from Rotherham, has 
OL,16,Fbeen charged with a public order       
OL,17,Foffence after being arrested on        
OL,18,FSaturday.                              
OL,20,FHe is due to appear in court on Monday.
